<lb n="0360a10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a1001">此明即是寶光明。</p>
<lb n="0360a11" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0360a1101">唵<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>特嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>惹<note place="inline">引</note>屹囉<note place="inline">二合</note>玉呬曳<note place="inline">二合引</note>
<lb n="0360a12" ed="T"/>吽<note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
<lb n="0360a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a1301">此明即是勝幡瓔珞。</p>
<lb n="0360a14" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0360a1401">唵<note place="inline">引</note>玉呬野<note place="inline">二合</note>賀<note place="inline">引</note>娑嚩日哩<note place="inline">二合</note>尼吽<note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
<lb n="0360a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a1501">此明即是大笑。</p>
<lb n="0360a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a1601">是等名為寶總持門。</p>
<lb n="0360a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a1701">復次四明曰。</p>
<lb n="0360a18" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0360a1801">唵<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>達哩摩<note place="inline">二合</note>玉呬野三摩曳<note place="inline"><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0360002" n="0360002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0360002" n="0360002"/>引<anchor xml:id="end0360002"/></note><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0360003" n="0360003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0360003" n="0360003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0360003" n="0360003"/>吽
<lb n="0360a19" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引一句</note><anchor xml:id="end0360003"/></p>
<lb n="0360a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a2001">此明即是金剛雲生。</p>
