<lb n="0360a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a2201">此明即是阿陀囉尼。</p>
<lb n="0360a23" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0360a2301">唵<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>玉呬野<note place="inline">二合</note>曼拏梨<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
<lb n="0360a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a2401">此明即是一切輪。</p>
