<lb n="0360a26" ed="T"/>句</note></p>
<lb n="0360a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a2701">此明即是轉大千。</p>
<lb n="0360a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a2801">是等名為法總持門。</p>
<lb n="0360a29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360a2901">復次四明曰。</p>
<pb n="0360b" xml:id="T18.0882.0360b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0360b01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0360b0101">唵<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>玉呬野<note place="inline">二合</note>葛哩摩<note place="inline">二合</note>三摩曳<note place="inline">引</note>吽
<lb n="0360b02" ed="T"/><note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
<lb n="0360b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360b0301">此明即是勝成就。</p>
<lb n="0360b04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0360b0401">唵<note place="inline">引</note>嚩日嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>玉呬野<note place="inline">二合</note>葛嚩際<note place="inline">引</note>吽<note place="inline">引一句</note></p>
<lb n="0360b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0360b0501">此明即是一切護。</p>
